reviewText:
A nice blu-ray set

I was expect two disc in this set but both videos and encoded to one Blu Ray.  I didn't like it at first but it saves on storage and organization of one more disc.

This videos were pretty good.  I was happy this concentrated on information instead of fluff.  The Professional video portion of this looks like it's for studying for the state massage exam.

I like it.

Simple: this BR is not HD! It is a BR disk, but it was shot with standard camera... and a very poor quality one (looks like VHS tape). I was conned, bamboozled and this should never be sold like this.
